## How to Run

1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies:
```bash
pip install pandas numpy scikit-learn matplotlib seaborn imbalanced-learn openpyxl
```
3. Open `Company_Success_Prediction.ipynb` in Jupyter Notebook or JupyterLab
4. Run cells sequentially — each section includes 
   interpretation markdown cells after every output

> **Note:** The original dataset file (`company_performance_culture.xlsx`) 
> is not included in this repository. The notebook structure, 
> methodology, and all outputs are fully documented and visible 
> in the notebook.

